snippet.title: Producer Foolishly Thinks AH is "Best" for Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
In a article from Deadline a producer says that AH is best for Aquaman 2 and that they weren't going to listen to "Johnny Depp Fans " you can read the article here: https://deadline.com/2021/07/amber-heard-aquaman-2-johnny-depp-fans-1234802845/

You can help me with the expenses of attending the VA trial by donating to my PayPal at: 
https://paypal.me/TammyTalksAbout?locale.x=en_US
